      • InputElement

        public InputElement(java.util.Date creationDate,
            java.lang.String name,
            ElementCategory category,
            Report report,
            boolean included,
            int position,
            java.lang.String contentType,
            boolean fullWidth,
            boolean pageBreakAfter)
        Constructor of input element specifying all the fields except the content
        Parameters:
        creationDate: - the date when the input element was created
        name: - the name of the input element
        category: - the category of the element
        report: - the report to which this element belongs
        included: - whether the input element is included or not in the publication of its parent Report.
        position: - the position of the input element in the report it belongs to
        contentType: - the type of the input content (considered as plain text if not recognized)
        fullWidth: - whether the element takes 2 column (full width) or only one column (half width)
        pageBreakAfter: - whether there should be a page break after the element
